#â”‹        Now done manually (this is changing right now so final version might not be yet documented)                                                                                                       â”‹
#â”‹                                                                                                                                                                                                          â”‹
#â”‹        sub termio: program-to-terminfo interface                                                                                                                                                         â”‹
#â”‹              note: Term::Cap has some major problems, so support for it was scrapped in the process                                                                                                      â”‹
#â”‹                    terminfo on the other hand, has a much better reliability record                                                                                                                      â”‹
#â”‹                                                                                                                                                                                                          â”‹
#â”‹                    plus records all the little term infos including width and height with great acurracy                                                                                                 â”‹
#â”‹                    furthermore, tput is a coreutil, so theres pretty much no chance of it being not installed unless you uninstalled it (why?)                                                           â”‹
#â”‹                    if for some odd reson tput is unavailable, this program CAN NOT RUN.  this should really never happen though!                                                                         â”‹
#â”‹                    dont confuse termio with termios! (POSIX::Termios)                                                                                                                                    â”‹
#â”‹                    comments.                                                                                                                                                                             â”‹
#â”‹                                                                                                                                                                                                          â”‹
