#â”‹                                                                                                                                                                                                          â”‹
#â”‹ This Project does NOT use tabs, please keep it that way by using spaces-from-tabs in your editors.                                                                                                       â”‹
#â”‹                                                                                                                                                                                                          â”‹
#â”‹                                                                                                                                                                                                          â”‹
#â”‹ Tabs are for typewriters and word processors, not programming                                                                                                                                            â”‹
#â”‹ Python programmers would argue it is essential, but space-indents are far more efficient, easily compressed and reformatted (last time i checked, PL's dont contain multiple fonts and sizes)            â”‹
#â”‹                                                                                                                                                                                                          â”‹
#â”‹ If we enter an era where programming languages (PLs) are multi-font/size/emphasis, then (and only then) would tabs make sense.                                                                           â”‹
#â”‹ Programmers should not be using variable-width fonts, but that is a discussion all on its own with many facts supporting it.                                                                             â”‹
#â”‹                                                                                                                                                                                                          â”‹
#â”‹ keep the vim line LAST (no whitespace lines either)                                                                                                                                                      â”‹
